{"id":233890,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-胡明军出狱后检查出多种疾病急需各界救/","date":"2012-06-22T06:01:04Z","modified":"2012-06-22T06:01:04Z","title":"维权网 | 胡明军出狱后检查出多种疾病急需各界救助(图)","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span> </span><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span>（维权网信息员梁飞报道）四川民主党人胡明军出狱后，去医院检查身体，彩超检查报告为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1,</span><span>二尖瓣反流</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>轻度</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">),2</span><span>主动脉瓣反流</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>轻度</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)3</span><span>左室舒张功能降低。心脏</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>小时趋势报告最低心率为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">51</span><span>，最高心率为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">128</span><span>，医生解释为：心肌炎引发的器质性、功能性心肌缺血、缺氧，属于心脏病的一种。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span> </p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">     </span></div>\n<div><span>胡明军于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>被以颠覆国家政权罪逮捕，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>刑满释放，服刑整整</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>年，刚入狱后因为营养不良，还需做繁重体力劳动，就患上了多种疾病，在狱中又得不到及时治疗，病情长期被延误，以至转化为器质性、功能性疾病。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">     </span></div>\n<div><span>据医生说：目前还没有治疗这类疾病的特效药，只能通过药物控制症状，不能做体力劳动，前期的治疗费用约需人民币壹万元以上，这笔巨大治疗费对刚刚出狱的胡明军来说根本无力支撑，胡明军的亲友希望社会各界能帮助胡明军度过难关。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>胡明军是中国民主党的四川党部骨干成员，曾以民主党的身份组织达州钢铁厂工人罢工维权，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月被达州警方拘留，一年后被当地法院以颠覆国家政权罪判处</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>年有期徒刑。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>胡明军原来自己做生意，因为推行民主人权致妻离子散，出狱后又没有医保和社保，没有固定收入，因此，生活难以为继，目前，生活主要靠亲友们的支援和救济，同时还面临求医治病的困境。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ZXXwmviqe6o/T-PpWTvaU_I/AAAAAAAAIsw/llzO4j7Evgk/s1600/P1020864.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ZXXwmviqe6o/T-PpWTvaU_I/AAAAAAAAIsw/llzO4j7Evgk/s320/P1020864.JPG\" width=\"235\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-8636558834298380972?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/f855b3c1P1020864.JPG-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}